===Adjective===
{{infl form|la|adjective|inter|comp|cat=comparatives}}

# [[inner]], [[#English|interior]].
# [[nearer]]

====Usage notes====
Although this adjective is the comparative form of {{term|inter|lang=la}}, there is no positive form.  The word {{term|inter|lang=la}} is an adverb and preposition, not an adjective.

